Curated by assistant editor Theresa Mallinson, Top of the Vox is a roundup of the best and biggest stories each week. The newsletter focuses on what everyone s talking about and what you may have missed out on. We also throw in some videos, cartoons, and whatever takes our fancy to get you in the mood for the weekend.Top of the Vox is also your chance to send us feedback (just reply to the mail) about what The Daily Vox is doing right, what we can improve on, and what you d like to see us cover next week.To receive Top of the Vox in your inbox every Friday morning, simply fill in your details. (We promise we won t share your email address with any third parties or send you gratuitous mail, ever. Pinky swear!)See you next Friday!